Iran ' s oil minister to visit Kuwait Sunday . Iran ' s Oil Minister Gholamreza Aghazadeh will start an official visit to Kuwait on Sunday , an Iranian diplomat said on Sunday . Ahgazadeh ' s two - day visit to the Gulf Arab state comes in response to an invitation by his counterpart Isa al - Mazeedi , the diplomat told Reuters without elaboration . The visit is the first by Aghazadeh to Kuwait since the 1991 Gulf War . 
